title: Morgan Newman
text:
Morgan Ram Newman (born 5 February 1986) is a South African <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player, currently playing with Western Province Premier League side <a href="Hamilton%20RFC%2C%20Sea%20Point">Hamiltons</a>.
He was born in <a href="Cape%20Town">Cape Town</a> and started his rugby career with , representing them at various age groups. In 2011, he moved to the for a short spell before joining the for a six-month spell later in that year.
